{"word":"Family","slug":"family","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Family</b> Of saints:<br/> - Blessed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=128&verse=3'>Psa 128:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=128&verse=6'>Psa 128:6</a> <br/> - Should be taught God's word<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=10'>Deu 4:10</a> <br/> - Worship God together<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=16&verse=19'>1Co 16:19</a> <br/> - Be duly regulated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=27'>Pro 31:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=3&verse=5'>1Ti 3:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=3&verse=12'>1Ti 3:12</a> <br/> - Live in unity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=45&verse=24'>Gen 45:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=133&verse=1'>Psa 133:1</a> <br/> - Live in mutual forbearance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=21'>Gen 50:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=22'>Mat 18:22</a> <br/> - Rejoice together before God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=26'>Deu 14:26</a> <br/> - Deceivers and liars should be removed from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=101&verse=7'>Psa 101:7</a> <br/> - Warned against departing from God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=29&verse=18'>Deu 29:18</a> <br/> - Punishment of irreligious<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=10&verse=25'>Jer 10:25</a> <br/> Good, exemplified:<br/> - Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=19'>Gen 18:19</a> <br/> - Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=2'>Gen 35:2</a> <br/> - J